* Never knew why
I loved you so *

33:44.923 --> 33:47.993
* Never did understand

33:48.026 --> 33:49.895
* Felt like lightning

33:49.928 --> 33:51.263
* Felt like quicksand

33:51.297 --> 33:52.264
* Loving you, baby

33:52.298 --> 33:59.105
* Wasn't in my plan...

