(guitar solo)

34:22.961 --> 34:24.963
(siren wails in the distance)

35:14.480 --> 35:16.248
What are

35:16.282 --> 35:20.719
their names, Father Bennett?

35:21.887 --> 35:23.655
(grunting)

35:36.067 --> 35:38.370
(rustling slows, grunting stops)

